{"tid":764484,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多人都用錯/撈亂「侯」同「候」字","createTime":"2018-08-02T04:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T06:35:12.000Z","uid":176311,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c4ef68e366d67f9cf4b0c7ecb7f53266922da8","tid":764484,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"侯同候明明個聲調唔同<br />\n候係第六聲，同後同音<br />\n而侯就第四聲，同喉同音<br />\n但就好多人都用錯或者撈亂<br />\n例如等候變咗等侯<br />\n侯城變咗候城(你可以話譯音都一樣，但就會變咗唔順口)<br />\n好多人可能會話明就得啦，使乜理咁多啫<br />\n但係我想講嘅係兩隻字係兩個完全唔同嘅字<br />\n根本意思係唔相通<br />\n而且連啲傳媒都用錯<br />\n我覺得個問題就幾嚴重下<br />\n所以我想大家都可以用啱啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40259637a75286e067c385139ccfb8a5a7a2507a","tid":764484,"uid":176311,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"利申：有強逼症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到錯別字會好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb319e071141e482fec72050e67cbd2d0f91af3d","tid":764484,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:24:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f12a032657d89f342218d994c4733c6681831b16","tid":764484,"uid":3138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:24:56.000Z","msg":"係有啲人打字唔睇清楚<br />\n已同己都可以用錯"},{"pid":"f7cb01ae841b3c6d135502df8b4197b4223b5157","tid":764484,"uid":176311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f12a032657d89f342218d994c4733c6681831b16","tid":764484,"uid":3138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:24:56.000Z","msg":"係有啲人打字唔睇清楚<br />\n已同己都可以用錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:25:40.000Z","msg":"我有啲同學連寫都寫錯"},{"pid":"d22dc96554f5c34cfc4c784c56cf6438364cc5fd","tid":764484,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"941a338a34544b409ac9d38da950841e9d450a04","tid":764484,"uid":60299,"like":0,"dis